	('aa060d77-0d88-4876-a06f-9188a04fa677', 'https://storage.googleapis.com/114system/part4/aa060d77-0d88-4876-a06f-9188a04fa677.mp3', 'Questions 1 through 3. Refer to the following announcement. Good morning, everyone. This is John, the marketing manager. I wanted to update you on our new product launch scheduled for next month. We expect this innovative gadget to significantly improve user experience and attract new customers. It is vital that all department heads prepare their teams for the presentation and marketing strategies that we will discuss in our next meeting. Please ensure that your reports are ready by the end of this week so we can move forward smoothly. Thank you for your cooperation!', 'american', '企業發展', 'intermediate', 1, '2025-09-30 00:00:48.539268', '2025-09-30 00:01:22.789447', NULL, '各位早安。我是行銷經理 John。我想更新一下我們計劃在下個月上市的新產品。這款創新小工具預計將大幅改善用戶體驗，並吸引新客戶。所有部門主管準備好他們的團隊參加我們的下一次會議中將要討論的報告和行銷策略是非常重要的。請確保你們的報告在這周末之前準備好，以便我們可以順利推進。謝謝你們的合作！'),
