	('f77ed6bf-dacb-439b-beda-e431269ac74c', 'https://storage.googleapis.com/114system/part4/f77ed6bf-dacb-439b-beda-e431269ac74c.mp3', 'Questions 1 through 3. Refer to the following announcement. Hello everyone, this is Lisa from the Marketing Department. We would like to remind you that the annual company picnic is scheduled for Friday, May 12th. Please mark your calendars! All employees are encouraged to attend for a day filled with fun activities, great food, and the chance to socialize with your colleagues. Don\'t forget to RSVP by next week so that we can finalize the headcount for catering. We hope to see everyone there and make this event a great success!', 'american', 'Company Event Announcement', 'intermediate', 1, '2025-09-29 19:00:32.727041', '2025-09-30 00:02:21.256521', NULL, '各位好，我是來自市場部的莉莎。我們想提醒大家，年度公司野餐定於5月12日星期五舉行。請標記您的日曆！所有員工都被鼓勵參加，享受充滿樂趣的活動、美妙的食物，並與同事社交。不要忘了在下週前回覆我們，以便我們能夠確認餐飲的參加人數。我們希望看到每個人到場，一起讓這個活動圓滿成功！'),
	('9ed671b2-d6d0-4920-a02d-e51536e0d38a', 'https://storage.googleapis.com/114system/part4/9ed671b2-d6d0-4920-a02d-e51536e0d38a.mp3', 'Questions 1 through 3. Refer to the following announcement. Good morning, everyone. This is a reminder that the annual company picnic will take place this Saturday at Riverside Park. All employees and their families are invited to join us for a day of fun and relaxation. Please remember to bring your own picnic blankets and favorite dishes to share. We will provide drinks and entertainment. Don\'t forget to RSVP by the end of the day if you haven\'t done so already to ensure we have enough food for everyone. Thank you!', 'american', 'Company Announcement', 'intermediate', 0, '2025-09-29 18:20:29.655007', '2025-09-30 00:02:35.392019', '題目有誤', '各位早安，這是提醒大家我們的年度公司野餐將於本週六在河濱公園舉行。所有員工及其家屬都被邀請來享受這一天的樂趣和放鬆。請記得攜帶自己的野餐毯和喜歡分享的菜餚。我們會提供飲料和娛樂節目。如果您還沒有請回覆RSVP，請記得在今天結束前完成，以確保我們有足夠的食物供應給每個人。謝謝！'),
	('56b04a7b-8e41-4583-bfae-e62320413486', 'https://storage.googleapis.com/114system/part4/56b04a7b-8e41-4583-bfae-e62320413486.mp3', 'Questions 1 through 3. Refer to the following announcement. Hello everyone, this is Lisa from the customer service department. I’d like to remind you that our annual product review meeting will be held next Thursday at 10 AM in the main conference room. Please make sure to prepare your reports and arrive at least 15 minutes early. We’ll be discussing last year’s sales performance and planning for the upcoming quarter. Your input is essential, so I hope to see all of you there. Thank you!', 'american', 'Company Announcement', 'intermediate', 1, '2025-09-29 08:21:09.828952', '2025-09-30 00:38:43.869851', NULL, '大家好，我是來自客戶服務部門的麗莎。我想提醒大家，我們的年度產品評審會議將在下週四上午十點於主會議室舉行。請確保準備好你的報告並至少提前15分鐘到達。我們將討論去年的銷售表現以及為接下來的季度做規劃。大家的意見很重要，期待看到每個人都來。謝謝！'),
	('7ac466a9-a17b-492d-a9cd-ee383244d44b', 'https://storage.googleapis.com/114system/part2/7ac466a9-a17b-492d-a9cd-ee383244d44b.mp3', 'What is the purpose of the new research project? A: It aims to enhance product performance. B: It is scheduled for next month. C: It requires more funding than expected.', 'american', 'Corporate Development', 'intermediate', 1, '2025-09-29 10:30:45.832699', '2025-09-29 17:09:02.994738', NULL, '這個新研究計畫的目的為何？ A: 它旨在提高產品性能。 B: 它定於下個月進行。 C: 它需要比預期更多的資金。'),
	('334ac617-c319-4201-867d-f05e56f8f405', 'https://storage.googleapis.com/114system/part4/334ac617-c319-4201-867d-f05e56f8f405.mp3', 'Questions 1 through 3. Refer to the following announcement. Hello everyone, this is a quick announcement about the upcoming company-wide meeting scheduled for next Tuesday at 10 AM. All employees are required to attend, as we will discuss our annual performance and future goals. Please make sure to prepare your reports ahead of time. If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to your respective managers. Thank you for your attention!', 'australian', 'Company Announcement', 'intermediate', 0, '2025-09-29 09:11:07.632011', '2025-09-30 00:41:01.410453', '', '各位好，這是一個有關即將舉行的公司全體會議的簡短公告，會議定於下週二上午10點。所有員工都必須參加，因為我們將討論年度績效和未來目標。請確保提前準備好您的報告。如果您有任何問題，隨時可以聯繫您各自的經理。謝謝您的關注！'),
	('0a47b03d-56e6-4675-8436-f3e3e71ac5a0', 'https://storage.googleapis.com/114system/part2/0a47b03d-56e6-4675-8436-f3e3e71ac5a0.mp3', 'What does the team need to enhance their product development process? A: They need more data analysis. B: They should reduce the project timeline. C: They require additional team members.', 'british', '企業發展', 'intermediate', 0, '2025-09-30 02:07:16.464954', '2025-09-30 02:07:16.464954', NULL, '團隊需要什麼來提升他們的產品開發流程？A: 他們需要更多的數據分析。B: 他們應該縮短專案時間表。C: 他們需要更多的團隊成員。'),
	('20620709-a837-47a5-b6b3-f59415c1f69b', 'https://storage.googleapis.com/114system/part4/20620709-a837-47a5-b6b3-f59415c1f69b.mp3', 'Questions 1 through 3. Refer to the following announcement. Good morning, everyone. This is a reminder about our company-wide meeting scheduled for this Thursday at 10 a.m. in the main conference room. Please make sure to arrive on time, as we will discuss important updates and the new project timelines. I encourage everyone to prepare any questions you might have, as there will be a Q&A session at the end. Thank you for your attention, and I look forward to seeing all of you there.', 'australian', 'Company Meeting Announcement', 'intermediate', 0, '2025-09-29 05:01:07.942372', '2025-09-30 00:40:56.244669', '', '早安，各位。這裡是提醒大家我們公司全體會議的通知，定於本週四上午10點在主會議室舉行。請確保準時到達，因為我們將討論重要的更新和新項目的時間表。我鼓勵每個人準備任何可能有的問題，因為會議結束時會有問答環節。謝謝大家的注意，希望能在那裡見到各位。'),
	('beee4676-60bc-4dd8-a89c-fa4e43f36196', 'https://storage.googleapis.com/114system/part4/beee4676-60bc-4dd8-a89c-fa4e43f36196.mp3', 'Questions 1 through 3. Refer to the following announcement.\\nHello everyone, this is a reminder that our company’s annual health and wellness fair will be held this Friday from 10 AM to 3 PM in the main conference hall. Employees will have the opportunity to participate in fitness classes, health screenings, and workshops on nutrition. We encourage all staff to attend as this is a great way to learn about maintaining a healthy lifestyle. Please make sure to register for the activities you are interested in. Thank you!', 'british', 'Company Announcement', 'intermediate', 0, '2025-09-29 06:55:11.298142', '2025-09-30 00:41:05.800439', '', '各位好，這是一則提醒，我們公司年度健康與福祉博覽會將於本週五上午十點至下午三點在主會議廳舉行。員工將有機會參加健身課程、健康檢查以及營養工作坊。我們鼓勵所有員工參加，因為這是一個了解維持健康生活方式的絕佳方式。請務必為您感興趣的活動報名。謝謝！'),
	('4cbeabe5-18be-4968-a21b-fd465febc06f', 'https://storage.googleapis.com/114system/part2/4cbeabe5-18be-4968-a21b-fd465febc06f.mp3', 'What is the focus of the new product development team?', 'british', 'Manufacturing', 'intermediate', 0, '2025-09-29 06:00:45.644344', '2025-09-29 15:28:48.245599', '題目有誤', '新產品開發團隊的重點是什麼？');
INSERT INTO `toeic_phrase` (`id`, `title`, `english_passage`, `chinese_translation`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `title_translation`) VALUES
	(1, 'put off', 'The meeting has been put off until Friday due to the manager\'s illness.', 'v. 推遲；延期。例句翻譯：經理生病了，會議已被推遲到週五。', '2025-09-28 20:35:48.422611', '2025-09-28 20:35:48.422611', NULL),
	(2, 'in accordance with', 'All employees must follow the company\'s guidelines in accordance with the safety regulations.', 'phr. 依照；根據。例句翻譯：所有員工都必須根據安全規定來遵守公司的指導方針。', '2025-09-28 20:35:48.429750', '2025-09-28 20:35:48.429750', NULL),
	(3, 'look into', 'We need to look into the customer\'s complaint and find a solution immediately.', 'phr. 調查；研究。例句翻譯：我們需要調查客戶的投訴並立即找到解決方案。', '2025-09-28 20:35:48.432762', '2025-09-28 20:35:48.432762', NULL),
	(4, 'account for', 'Online sales account for over 60% of our total revenue this quarter.', 'phr. 佔(某比例)；解釋。例句翻譯：線上銷售佔了本季度總收入的60%以上。', '2025-09-28 20:35:48.435762', '2025-09-28 20:35:48.435762', NULL),
	(5, 'take on', 'I am willing to take on more responsibilities to help the team succeed.', 'phr. 承擔；接受(工作或責任)。例句翻譯：我願意承擔更多責任，以幫助團隊取得成功。', '2025-09-28 20:35:48.441568', '2025-09-28 20:35:48.441568', NULL);
